column5: Well Guys I was able to get my hands on this video from deerdummy.com. I recommend it to anyone that wants to the start processing there own deer. I gives you step by step instructions and what your best cuts are and where. the DVD is called "follow the bone deer cutting" from deerdummy.com. If you were thinking about doing it yourself i recommend starting here. Just thought i'd share this great video with people that may want to start processing there own deer.
